title: 2009 - Deluxe Edition - Shine a Light - The Rolling Stones
description:
The Shine A Light soundtrack is available in three versions: the regular edition, deluxe edition, and collector's USB stick. Browse these and other albums from the Rolling Stones.


DELUXE VERSION - 2 disc set, featuring 22 tracks with expanded packaging. Includes every track from the film, plus four bonus tracks from the shows that were not included in the film- "Paint It Black", "Little T&A", "Shine A Light" and "I'm Free"
